HEADWORD: Swordsman
<hw>Swords"man</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Swordsmen</plw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>.</plu> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A soldier; a
fighting man.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One skilled of a use of the sword; a professor of
the science of fencing; a fencer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Swordsmanship</ent>⟦br⟧
